    <title type="text">ANCIENT ROME LIVE: A new way to learn about Rome's past</title>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a href="http://www.ancientromelive.org/"><span
      style="letter-spacing: 0em;">ANCIENT ROME LIVE</span>:<strong> </strong>A
      new way to learn about Rome's past</a><br /><blockquote class="tr_bq"><img
      alt="http://static1.squarespace.com/static/5360d035e4b0ec04b0fdcce6/t/553663aee4b0819833f2fbf0/1430284270749/?format=1500w"
